======================================================================
D(T,x) = F(T,x) - F(T^op,x) [ANTI-PALINDROMIC PART]
======================================================================
D_k = F_k - F_{d-k}, so D_k + D_{d-k} = 0 (anti-palindromic)
F = (G + D)/2 where G is palindromic and D is anti-palindromic

n=4:
  F=[1, 0, 0, 0], D=[1, 0, 0, -1], H=1
